long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Provides fast pleasing display of multiple sites that you can select when new tab is selected. Find any MP3, check weather and news or email with one click or add your own favorites.

Sites can be edited, deleted, or rearranged by dragging them to desired locations.
